Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:22.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}打破了原有的安靜祥和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:25.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}無所顧忌地大肆爭執
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不給對方以喘息的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:33.34,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不給彼此以留下的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:39.26,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我一直喜愛你凝視我的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:47.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}也始終懷念你帶給我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那時整個世界只有我們二人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那時我們二人就是整個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:01:01.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我還是會像過去一樣顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:09.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我還是會為你放棄所有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:17.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我還是會像過去一樣顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:25.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}只是為你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:32.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:20.37,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}We broke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:22.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}Everything that was right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:25.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}We both enjoyed a good fight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And we solved
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}All the holes we had to breathe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:33.34,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}To make the other one leave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:39.26,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And I loved the way you looked at me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:47.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And I miss the way you made me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:49.40,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}When we were alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}When we were alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:01:01.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And I'll shiver like I used to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:09.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And I'll leave him just for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:17.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}And I'll shiver like I used to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:25.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}Just for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:32.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs37}Like I used to
